[07:52:13.015] [INFO ]     I do not have access to NovaAI's specific, up-to-date internal employee handbook or HR policies regarding Paid Time Off (PTO). PTO accrual rates, carry-over limits, and approval processes can vary by location, employment contract type (e.g., full-time vs. contractor), and tenure, and these details are subject to change.
    
    To get the accurate and official policy:
